The first Madrid Derby of this season will be played on Saturday night. Atletico host Real, in what promises to be a fascinating encounter at the Wanda Metropolitano. Zinedine Zidane’s come into the fixture top of LaLiga, only one point ahead of second-placed Atletico. Kick-off is 8 pm West African time. Saturday, September 28
